TweetPoll - Manage Twitter Polls.

Using:
Devise and Omniauth for Authentication
CanCan for Authorization
RSpec, spork, autotest and Factory-Girl for testing

On OSX, use autotest-fsevent to save battery. On linux, autotest-inotify.
autotest-growl is also awsome :D

